summary.raw:
Rename AddSkeleton to UpdateSkeletonInWorld

summary.raw:
Fix for adding links after a model has been constructed

This is a proposed fix for adding nodes to a skeleton once the skeleton is added to the world. This is done by first removing the skeleton if it has already been added to the world and then adding it back.
